        "subject": "LU-19246 tests: Error if FORCE_LARGE_NID=true w/o ipv6",
        "message": "LU-19246 tests: Error if FORCE_LARGE_NID=true w/o ipv6\n\nTrigger an error if FORCE_LARGE_NID=true but an ipv6 NID is not\nconfigured. This will allow us to detect cases where we request ipv6\ntesting but the environment is not configured for it.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I1b9508ab2e94b2881e0024307ac34f805a32c677\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60587\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
